---

# 🔹 UPSC

Functions:

* Recruitment for civil services
* Conduct examinations

---

# 🔴 Finance Commission

Functions:

* Tax distribution between Centre & States

Appointed every:
👉 5 years

---

# 🔹 Comptroller & Auditor General (CAG)

Functions:

* Audit government accounts

Called:
👉 Guardian of Public Purse

---

# 🔵 NITI Aayog

Replaced:
👉 Planning Commission (2015)

Functions:

* Policy think tank
* Cooperative federalism

📌 Non-constitutional & non-statutory body.

---

# 🔹 NHRC

### Full Form:

National Human Rights Commission

Type:
👉 Statutory body

Purpose:

* Protect human rights

---

# 🔴 SEBI

### Full Form:

Securities and Exchange Board of India

Functions:

* Regulates stock market

Type:
👉 Statutory body

