# 🔹 Difference Between Constitutional & Statutory Bodies

| Feature    | Constitutional | Statutory      |
| ---------- | -------------- | -------------- |
| Created by | Constitution   | Parliament law |
| Security   | Higher         | Lower          |
| Example    | UPSC           | NHRC           |

---

# 🔹 Important Facts

| Body       | Type           |
| ---------- | -------------- |
| UPSC       | Constitutional |
| ECI        | Constitutional |
| NHRC       | Statutory      |
| NITI Aayog | Non-statutory  |

